            <br>
              <br>
                <div class="section-text " style="display:flex;flex-direction: column;align-items: center;">
                  Sri Lanka is known for its tropical climate, scenic landscapes, and pristine beaches that stretch for miles. With
                  crystal-clear waters, soft sandy beaches, and a laid-back vibe, the island's coastline is a true paradise for beach
                  lovers. Whether you're looking to soak up the sun, catch a wave, or enjoy a relaxing stroll along the shore, there's a
                  beach in Sri Lanka that's perfect for you.
                  <br>
                    <br>
                      Some of the most popular beaches in Sri Lanka include Unawatuna, Mirissa, Hikkaduwa, and Bentota, each offering a unique
                      experience. For water sports enthusiasts, there's surfing, scuba diving, and snorkeling, while those seeking peace and
                      tranquility can indulge in yoga or meditation on the beach. The beachside restaurants and bars offer a variety of local
                      and international cuisine, with fresh seafood being a highlight.
                      <br>
                        <br>
                          With so many beaches to choose from, a trip to Sri Lanka wouldn't be complete without some beach time. Whether you're
                          looking for adventure, relaxation, or a little bit of both, the island's beaches are waiting for you to discover their
                          beauty and charm.
